      <td> <font face="Verdana" size="-1">I formerly kept a running journal of my travels and adventures in the lands of Norrath at the Knight Watch but a tragic data loss has erased my logs. I kept a local copy of my journal so I shall begin reposting the chapters of my life here. Enjoy. =)</font></td>
